<ab facs="#facs_177_r1l4">burg vnd Smoel ſprıncʒ ʒwen Juden bey vns wonhaftıg / <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_177_r1l5">vnd ʒu eẅch gefüret <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wır <expan>Burkarte<ex>n</ex></expan> Reıkarcʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_177_r1l6"><expan>hof<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu eẅch <expan>ſend<ex>en</ex></expan> dem wır befolhen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_177_r1l7">eẅch <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan> . Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch mıt fleıſſ VVas derſelb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_177_r1l8"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu dıſem mal von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_177_r1l9"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan> . Daʒ Jr Jm das
<del rend="strikethrough">rinn</del> <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd gütlıch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_177_r1l10">eẅch <expan>fertıg<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet als wır eẅch <expan>wolgetrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır </ab>
