</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_177" id="87v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Hasling<ex>er</ex></expan> und dem rate der stat zum Stein</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<add><expan>Hassling<ex>er</ex></expan></add> und
                            <expan>l<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns ist <expan>furkome<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        wie <expan>Gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan> von Weissemburg und Smoel Sprincz,
                        zwen juden bey uns wonhaftig, <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und zu
                        ewch gefüret <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> sein.
                            <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wir <expan>Burkarte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Reikarczhof<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> zu ewch <expan>send<ex>en</ex></expan>, dem
                        wir befolhen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit ewch
                            <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu <expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan>; und
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch mit fleiss, was derselb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir
                        im das <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und gütlich <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
                        von ewch <expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet, als wir ewch
                                <expan>wolgetrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Das
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir mit <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        umb ewch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
